sec.p:
RMSSD = \sqrt{\frac{1}{N-1}\sum_{j-1}^{N-1}(RRi_{j} - RRi_{j+1})^2}
RMSSD=1N−1∑j−1N−1(RRij−RRij+1)2
- Equation 1

SD1 = \sqrt{2SDNN^{2} - 2SD2^{2}}
SD1=2SDNN2−2SD22
- Equation 2

SD2 = \sqrt{2SDNN^{2} - \frac{1}{2}SDSD^{2}}
SD2=2SDNN2−12SDSD2
- Equation 3

